│                                                                              │
│  ### Salary Ranges in Australia                                              │
│                                                                              │
│  - **Entry Level** (1-3 years): Average $110,620                             │
│  - **Mid-Level**: $130,000-$150,000+ range                                   │
│  - **Senior Level** (8+ years): Average $179,268                             │
│  - **Overall Range**: $110,000-$190,000+                                     │
│                                                                              │
│  Note: Salaries vary by location, seniority level, platform specialization,  │
│  and contract type.                                                          │
