│                                                                              │
│  For Staff-level positions:                                                  │
│  - Critical thinking and judgment                                            │
│  - Listening and empathy                                                     │
│  - Communication skills                                                      │
│  - Complex project leadership                                                │
│  - Technical mentorship                                                      │
│  - Strategic guidance                                                        │
│                                                                              │
