│  ## Essential Professional and Leadership Competencies                       │
│                                                                              │
│  ### Leadership and Strategic Thinking                                       │
│                                                                              │
│  #### Critical Thinking and Judgment                                         │
│                                                                              │
│  Staff Data Engineers must demonstrate superior analytical capabilities:     │
│                                                                              │
│  - **Problem Analysis**: Breaking down complex problems into manageable      │
│  components                                                                  │
│  - **Root Cause Analysis**: Identifying fundamental causes rather than       │
│  addressing symptoms                                                         │
│  - **Trade-off Evaluation**: Assessing technical trade-offs and their        │
│  implications (performance vs. cost, scalability vs. simplicity)             │
│  - **Strategic Vision**: Understanding how technical decisions align with    │
│  organizational goals                                                        │
│  - **Decision Documentation**: Capturing decisions and reasoning for future  │
│  reference (Architecture Decision Records)                                   │
│                                                                              │
